{"tid":125210,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"每日失眠 開始睇唔透呢個世界 點解有女仲咁","createTime":"2017-02-18T09:41:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-19T18:46:02.000Z","uid":72212,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0c998823f333aab05db66e0804c9d0efe163c25a","tid":125210,"uid":72212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T09:41:37.000Z","msg":"岩岩起身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n身體又愈來愈痛<br />\n仲有幾日又要交租 <br />\n生活唔到我都唔知點算<br />\n又無人幫 不過咁多個傾到心事既都有幾個既<br />\n訓一粒鍾醒幾粒鍾<br />\n又成日諗番起之前啲野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就黎想問有無免費心理醫生<br />\n好大壓力好辛苦<br />\n呻完啦 好好多啦 <br />\n<br />\n不過我早排遇到啲狗公過唔狗公既價值觀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n定係90後既價值唔同左<br />\n講真既 熟左我無所謂<br />\n暫時講住兩個故事先啦<br />\n雖然都係無人幫 純粹比人笑下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n1.咁有一日有個人密我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢就話想幫我既 但佢講明有女朋友 同慢慢加條件<br />\n但佢幫既定義 要搞野 <br />\n但佢話佢接受到亂扑 只要佢條女唔知<br />\n我就好奇咁啦 其實你做呢啲野之前有無諗過你條女?<br />\n佢就同我講 因為未食過無毛既妹妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n果一刻 我為佢條女默哀左一分鍾<br />\n我都曾經比人帽過 仲要當面做呢啲野<br />\n點解一個男人有女朋友仲可以咁..<br />\n你話無女想搵人扑 我都話比到藉口自己<br />\n但有女仲要搵其他女扑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咩道理黎?<br />\n最後我決定 唔覆 封埋 因為好煩<br />\n講真既 過唔到亂扑野呢關<br />\n<br />\n2.呢個有圖有真相啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好搞笑 我早幾篇文都講自住有養寵物既<br />\n話上黎玩狗 話好鍾意小動物<br />\n呢下我信左 但無啦啦問我有無梳化<br />\n玩乜狗要有床有梳化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係未當我蠢成咁？<br />\n最後呢條仔 消失左<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/18/173445_aad93faa0e4316124597487ced0aa4d5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F18%2F173445_aad93faa0e4316124597487ced0aa4d5.jpg&h=a2107b40&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OEf6201.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOEf6201.jpg&h=eed15ce4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有好多花生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/iambobo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fiambobo&d=UYGl2U%2FUD6QdVJGaYMmpaBv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=bca26d50\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/iambobo</a>"},{"pid":"1e479f5b20ffda61dcc5770473d88d85646a2614","tid":125210,"uid":81657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T10:27:39.000Z","msg":"正正經經揾個男朋友啦，係度叫人加telegram 同揾厹無分別"},{"pid":"80c12af74fc4ec299c8d7975c516d4cb8d14e6a5","tid":125210,"uid":36341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T11:58:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>岩岩起身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n身體又愈來愈痛<br />\n仲有幾日又要交租 <br />\n生活唔到我都唔知點算<br />\n又無人幫 不過咁多個傾到心事既都有幾個既<br />\n訓一粒鍾醒幾粒鍾<br />\n又成日諗番起之前啲野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就黎想問有無免費心理醫生<br />\n好大壓力好辛苦<br />\n呻完啦 好好多啦 <br />\n<br />\n不過我早排遇到啲狗公過唔狗公既價值觀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n定係90後既價值唔同左<br />\n講真既 熟左我無所謂<br />\n暫時講住兩個故事先啦<br />\n雖然都係無人幫 純粹比人笑下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n1.咁有一日有個人密我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢就話想幫我既 但佢講明有女朋友 同慢慢加條件<br />\n但佢幫既定義 要搞野 <br />\n但佢話佢接受到亂扑 只要佢條女唔知<br />\n我就好奇咁啦 其實你做呢啲野之前有無諗過你條女?<br />\n佢就同我講 因為未食過無毛既妹妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n果一刻 我為佢條女默哀左一分鍾<br />\n我都曾經比人帽過 仲要當面做呢啲野<br />\n點解一個男人有女朋友仲可以咁..<br />\n你話無女想搵人扑 我都話比到藉口自己<br />\n但有女仲要搵其他女扑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咩道理黎?<br />\n最後我決定 唔覆 封埋 因為好煩<br />\n講真既 過唔到亂扑野呢關<br />\n<br />\n2.呢個有圖有真相啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好搞笑 我早幾篇文都講自住有養寵物既<br />\n話上黎玩狗 話好鍾意小動物<br />\n呢下我信左 但無啦啦問我有無梳化<br />\n玩乜狗要有床有梳化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係未當我蠢成咁？<br />\n最後呢條仔 消失左<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/18/173445_aad93faa0e4316124597487ced0aa4d5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F18%2F173445_aad93faa0e4316124597487ced0aa4d5.jpg&h=a2107b40&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OEf6201.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOEf6201.jpg&h=eed15ce4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有好多花生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/iambobo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fiambobo&d=UYGl2U%2FUD6QdVJGaYMmpaBv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=bca26d50\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/iambobo</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n潔身自愛呀"},{"pid":"7db17324bb2fbe155f0dd7cdb6e379188806cd44","tid":125210,"uid":72212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T12:34:24.000Z","msg":"有呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n自己生活左咁多年<br />\n不過我唔明白男人諗乜<br />\n明明有個好好既女朋友都唔珍惜.."},{"pid":"5417855e0d1ee56f64016025e52a51da6581771f","tid":125210,"uid":72212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T13:24:37.000Z","msg":"呢兩個都係巴打黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔係我自己識架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過唔知佢地ac名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbfc427ca84edb39270e202bc8255a7ab9e33690","tid":125210,"uid":32842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T22:56:53.000Z","msg":"物以類聚"},{"pid":"9052806e193a356ab37a44faa6510d14d4306df1","tid":125210,"uid":12886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T23:19:21.000Z","msg":"絲打小心啲wo